text: Mofiz Uddin Talukder is a Jatiya Party (Ershad) politician and the former Member of Parliament of Sirajganj-5. ==Career== Talukder was elected to parliament from Sirajganj-5 as a Jatiya Party candidate in 1986. ==References== Category:Jatiya Party politicians Category:Living people Category:4th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:People from Sirajganj District
title: Mofiz Uddin Talukder
